$interpreted: Roger: Didn't I tell you guys to pay attention to details when gathering intel? We're lucky I discovered the kingdom bodyguards early.
Roger: If not for that, we're all getting busted today!
Irritated Henchman: ... It's a snap decision by the convoy to hire the kingdom army. You can't blame us for that...

Roger: Oh, so you want to talk back!?
You guys find life a bit too easy these days, don't you?

Roger: Back off;
I'll settle this score later...
Roger: Why are you here again, you freak?
Aosta: Heard your conditions have worsened lately. Just here to show my regards.
Roger: Stop using those big words. I know you're only interested in dissecting me.

Aosta: A regular monster bite victim would have mutated and gone berserk already.
You, on the other hand, have been able to suppress
Aosta: that mutation by amputating your right arm yourself. That is indeed worth researching.
Roger: I dare you to try!
Roger: You still wanna continue? If we keep going, you might be able to hold me down, but not before I lop off some of your limbs!

Aosta: Forget it; I have time to spare and wait. 
Besides, it's not like you don't have any weaknesses.
Roger: What do you mean?
Aosta: There's definitely someone by your side that is very important to you. So much so that her existence gives you the willpower to hold on to your senses.
Aosta: If I capture that person, you can do nothing but obey my requests.
Roger: If you dare lay a finger on her, your face better be prepared to say hi to my knife!

Aosta: You wield your knife, 
and you no longer have hands to protect that person anymore.
Roger: You...!
Kittyeyes: Brother Roger, the others told me that you just...
Kittyeyes: Aosta!?
Kittyeyes: Brother Roger, what just happened?
Roger: Nothing. You don't have to worry about me. Everything is fine...
